Package: reportingGuidelines
Type: Package
Title: The Reporting Guidelines for various Research communication outputs for R 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wojciech Francuzik
Maintainer: Wojciech Francuzik <wolass@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides Rmarkdown templates for easy and compact
    reference when writing scientific reports. The initial idea was to help 
    with the conformity (adherence to standards and published guidelines) 
    when preparing the reproducible reports to be published in the scientific journals. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/wolass/reportingGuidelines
BugReports: https://github.com/wolass/reportingGuidelines/issues
